OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSchools in England told to 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Flimit uniform costs        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Parents in England must be allowed to  
OL,6, buy some uniform from High Street shops
OL,7, as well as school suppliers, according 
OL,8, to new government rules.               
OL,10,FSecond-hand items should be made       
OL,11,Favailable and the cost of anything     
OL,12,Fbranded must be kept to a minimum.     
OL,14,FEducation Secretary Nadhim Zahawi said 
OL,15,Fthe legally binding guidelines would   
OL,16,Fmake uniforms "far more affordable".   
OL,18,FThe move has been welcomed by education
OL,19,Funions - but child poverty campaigners 
OL,20,Fsay more action is needed.             
